sourcesContent: import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { PassengerService } from './../api/services/passenger.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-register-passenger', templateUrl: './register-passenger.component.html', styleUrls: ['./register-passenger.component.css'] }) export class RegisterPassengerComponent implements OnInit { constructor(private passengerService: PassengerService) { } ngOnInit(): void { } register() { this.passengerService.registerPassenger(); } }
